\id 2PE - Gamo Full Bible final version
\h 2Phexroosa Kiita
\toc1 Phexroosi Xaafida Nam7anththo Kiita
\toc2 2Phexroosa Kiita
\toc3 2Phex
\mt1 Phexroosi
\mt2 Xaafida Nam7anththo Kiita
\imt1 Giddo Qofa
\ip Hawaare Phexroosi nam7anththo kiitaa xaafiday dumma dummason diza beni ammaniza asaassa; he iza kiitaas ayfe yo7oy wordo astamaareta iita oosonne istta timirte gaason yida bala de7o asay aggana malassa. He wode medhettida metota birshanaas dandayanay Yesus Kirstoosa kase ba ayfera be7idaytanne izi tamaarsishin ba hayththan siyida asati immida timirte baggara Xoossa gishshassinne Godaa Yesus Kirstoosa gishshas tumu erateth demmo. Xaafezi harappeka lo7eththi naagettiday, «Kirstoosi haa simmi yeenna» giza wordo timirte gishshassa; izi hessa gishshas yootishe, «Kirstoosi eleli simmi yontta mala iza diggizay asi wurikka ba nagarappe simmidi attana malappe attiin oonikka dhayana mala koyontta gishshassa» gees.
\iot Ha Maxaafay Oykkida Kumeththa Qofa
\io1 Geloso \ior 1:1-2\ior*
\io1 Ammanizayta xeygeteth \ior 1:3-21\ior*
\io1 Wordo astamaareta \ior 2:1-22\ior*
\io1 Kirstoosas nam7anththo yuussa \ior 3:1-18\ior*
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 Yesus Kirstoosa oosanchchanne izan Hawaare Simoona gidida Phexroosappe, nu Godaappenne nu dhale Yesus Kirstoosappe beettida xilloteththa baggara nu demmida ammano mala bonchchettida ammano demmidaytoo!
\v 2 Xoossaanne nu Godaa Yesusa eron kiyateththinne saroy inttes gido.
\s1 Xoossan Xeygetti Izan Dooreteth
\p 
\v 3 Ba bonchchoninne ba kiyateththan nuna xeygidayssa nuni iza erida gishshas iza Xoossateththaa wolqqay de7ossinne Xoos goynnanaas nuus koshshizaaz ubbaa immides.
\v 4 Ba bonchchoninne ba kiyateththan bonchcho wogay dizayssanne keehi gita gidida iza hidotaa nuni demmidos; heytantta baggara intte iita amo gaason hayssa ha alamezan diza dhayoppe kessi ekkidi Xoossateththa hanozappe izara gishettizaadentta gidideta.
\p 
\v 5 Hessa gaason hayssafe kaalliza miishshati inttes gujettana mala ane minnite. Ammano bolla kiyateth, kiyateththa bolla erateth,
\v 6 erateththa bolla bana haaro, bana haaro bolla dandayan mineteth, dandayan mineteththa bolla Xoossas goyno,
\v 7 Xoossas goyno bolla ishanttara doseteth, ishanttara doseteththa bolla siiqo gujjite.
\v 8 Hayti inttes dari dizaaz gidikko heyti inttena intte Godaa Yesus Kirstoosa eron go7aynne ayfey bayndayta gidontta mala naagana.
\v 9 Hayti ha miishshati baynda asi gidikko haahon diza miish demmontta qooqe asa mala; hessaadey kase aadhdhida ba nagarappe geeyidayssaka balettides.
\p 
\v 10 Ta ishatoo! Hessa gishshas intte xeygettidayssanne doorettidayssa shaakki eranaas keehi amottizayta gidite; intte hessaththo ooththiko mulekka dhuphetteketa.
\v 11 Intte hessaththo hankko mernaappe mernaas diza nu Godaa Yesus Kirstoosa kawoteththan gelanaas inttes kumeththa maatay imettana.
\p 
\v 12 Intte hayta ha yo7ota eridinne intte erida tumaan minni de7ikkoka heyta tani inttena qofsanaappe guye giikke.
\v 13 Tani paxa diza wode ubbaan inttena ubba wode denththeththanayssi bessizaaz misatidi taas beettees.
\v 14 Nu Godaa Yesus Kirstoosi taas qonccisida mala tani hayssa alamezappe elelada hayqqanayssa ta erays.
\v 15 Tani ha7i minettizay ta hayqqada inttefe shaakettidaappe guye intte hayta ha yo7ota ubba wode qoppana malassa.
\s1 Kirstoosa Bonchcho Ba Ayfen Be7ida Markkata
\p 
\v 16 Godaa Yesus Kirstoosa wolqqafe izas yuussa gishshas nu inttes yootida wode nuni nu ayfera iza bonchchoza be7idi markkattoos attiin asi coo mela medhdhi ekkidi gene haasayza haysi7e mala gidenna.
\v 17 «Tani izan ufayettizaadey ta dosiza ta naazi hayssa» giza qaala giirissay gita bonchchora izas yida wode izi Xoossaa Aawappe bonchchonne gitateth ekkides.
\v 18 Nuni izara anjjettida zumaa bolla dishe hayssa saloppe ha yida giirissaa nuni nu hayththan siyidos.\x - \xo 1:17-18 \xt Mato 17:1-5; Mar 9:2-7\x*
\p 
\v 19 Hessi wurikka kase nabeti yootidayssi tumu gididayssa lo7eththi qonccisees; hessa gishshas intte dhumason diza xomppes lo7eththi naagettizayssa mala kase nabeti yootidayssa lo7eththi naagettite. Intte hessaththo ooththanay gadey wonttanaas, bazzoy zo7ana gakkanaassinne wonti maaththa xoolinttezi intte wozinan poo7ana gakkanaassa.
\v 20 Intte harappe aaththi qoppanaas bessizay Geeshsha Maxaafan diza tinbite qaalaan yootettida ay miishshika oonikka baas misatida mala birshanaas bessenna.
\v 21 Ay tinbiteykka asa shene mala mulekka yibeenna; gido attiin tinbitey wurikka Xillo Ayanay kaaleththiin iza kaallida asati Xoossafe ekkidi yootidaaza.
\c 2
\s1 Wordo Astamaareta
\p 
\v 1 Gido attiin beni wode wordo nabeti dere giddon dizayssa mala hessaththoka ha7i intte giddon wordo astamaareti de7andettes; heytantti asa dhayssiza wordo timirte qotara diccana mala ooththeettes; bana ashshida Godaakka kaddidi bana eeson dhayssizaaz ba bolla eheettes.
\v 2 Hessa gaason daro asay yeellachchiza istta ogeza kaallees; he istta oosoza gaason tumaa ogey cayettees.
\v 3 Heyti wordo astamaareti miishshas gaphigaphiza gishshas barkka medhdhi ekkida yo7o yooti yootidi inttes dizaaz baas bonqqi ekkeettes; beni beniisoppe pirday isttas giigetti uttides; addafe istta dhayoy naagees.
\p 
\v 4 Haray attoshin nagara ooththida kiitanchchatas Xoossi mishettontta istti ciimma gidida dhuma olla giddon de7idi pirda gallas gakkanaas naagettana mala gede gaannamen yeggides.
\v 5 Hessaththoka xilloteththa gishshas sabaake gidida Nohe hankko laappun asatara ashshidi Xoossas goynnontta asati diza alameza bolla dhayssiza haaththe ehishe qadhettidi kase he wode alameza maaribeenna.\x - \xo 2:5 \xt Medhe 6:1—7:24\x*
\v 6 Qasseka Xoos goynnonttayta qaxxayanaas ubbaas leemiso gidana mala Sodoomeynne Gamoora katamati bidinth gidana gakkanaassinne xuugetti dhayana gakkanaas istta bolla pirdides.\x - \xo 2:6 \xt Medhe 19:24\x*
\p 
\v 7 Wogay baynda yeellachchiza ooso ooththiza asata ooson ubba wode so77u gishe diza xillo Looxe gidikko ashshi ekkides.\x - \xo 2:7 \xt Medhe 19:1-16\x*
\v 8 He xillo addezi istta giddon dishin gallas gallas izi be7izayssaninne siyizayssan he wogay baynda asata oosozan iza shemppoya waayettadus.
\v 9 Histtiin hessi wurikka hessa mala gidikko Goday baas goynnishe diza asata paaceppe ashshanayssanne nagaranchchatakka wostti qaxxayanaakkonne pirda gallassas wostti istta naagidi gaththanaakko hessa izi erees guussa.
\p 
\v 10 Harappeka heyti tuna gidida ba asho amo kaallizaytanne Xoossa Godateth kadhizayta pirda gallassas naagi woththides. Heyti wordo astamaareti istti xalatanne otoranchchata gidida gishshas salo bolla isttas godateththi dizayta cayishe babbettenna.
\v 11 Kiitanchchati isttafe bollara wolqqaynne godateththi dizayta gidikkoka Godaa sinththan istta bolla kadhe qaala kessi mootettenna.
\p 
\v 12 Heyti wordo astamaareti gidikko baas erettontta ixxida miish ubbaa cash cayeettes; heytantti narxan oykettanaassinne hayqqanaas yelettida; coo mela ba shenen dizaytanne qofay baynda do7ata mala; do7ati coo mela dhayzayssaththo isttika mulera dhayana.
\v 13 Qoho ooso ooththida gishshas istti mulera ba ooso waaga ekkana; istta ufayssi seeta gallas maththoteththinne wogay baynda buraqo; istti hessa mala wogay baynda gufan inttenara issife xeygettiza wode as baleththiza ba asho oosozan istti iitanne yeellachchizayta.
\v 14 Isttas nagara oosoppe naagettontta amottiza ayfey dees; isttas nagara ooso siiqiza amoteththi ay wodekka simmenna. Ammanon buro minni eqqontta asata baleththeettes; miishshas gaphigapheettes; istti qanggettidayta.
\v 15 Istti suure ogeza aggidi dhayda; iita ooso ooththidi demmiza miish siiqida Bi7oore naa Bala7aame oge biidi balettida.
\v 16 Bala7aamey gidikko ba ooththida nagara gishshas seerettides shin haasaya erontta hareya asa qaalan izas haasayada he nabeza balaappe seera zaaradus.
\p 
\v 17 Heyti he asati haaththi baynda pulttota; gote carkon biza shaara mala; istta sakkanna dhumay naagees.
\v 18 Kase bala garsan diza asata giddofe kessi ekki yiidi daro gam7ontta asata; hada gidida otoro qaala haasayan, asho amoninne layman baleththeettes.
\v 19 «Intte wozzettana» gishe inttes ufays immeettes; xoonettida asi bana xoonidaades aylle gidi haarettizayssaththo isttika baas nagaras aylle.
\v 20 Nu Godaanne nuna ashshida Yesus Kirstoosa eridi ha alameza tunateththaafe kessi ekkidaappe guye qasseka guye simmidi he kase tunateththaan xoonettidi gelikko isttas kaseyssafe guyeyssi aadho iita gidana.
\v 21 Istti xilloteththa oge shaakki eridaappe guye isttas imettida geeshsha azazozappe guye simmanaappe istti kase he xilloteththa ogeza erontta aggidaakko isttas lo7okkoshin.
\v 22 «Kanay ba cooyida cooshshaa maanaas guye simmees.» Hessaththoka, «Guddunththi meecettidi guye simmi urqqan genderettees» geetettiza tumu leemisoy istta bolla gakkides.\x - \xo 2:22 \xt Leemi 26:11\x*
\c 3
\s1 Godaa Yesus Kirstoosas Nam7anththo Yuus
\p 
\v 1 Ta siiqotoo! Tani inttes xaafishin hayssi nam7anththo kiita; tani inttes nam7u kiitatakka xaafiday hayta ha yo7ota akeeki ekkidi intte suure qofa qoppana mala inttena beegoththanaassa.
\v 2 Hayssafe kase geeshsha nabeti yootida qaalanne qasse Hawaareta baggara intte demmida nu Godaanne nuna ashshidayssa azazo intte yuushshi qoppana mala ta koyays.
\p 
\v 3 Hara ubbaafe kasetidi hayssa yuushshi qopite; wurseththa gallassatan qidhizaytinne ba iita amo kaallishe as kadhizayti yaana.\x - \xo 3:3 \xt Yuhu 18\x*
\v 4 Istti, «Godaa Yesusi, ‹Yaana› giza hidotay yootettibeennee? Histtiin izi awan dizee? Beni nu aawati hayqqoosofe haa simmiin, haniza miishshi wurikka medhettoosoppe haa simmiin hekko kase ba diza mala dees» geettes.
\v 5 Heyti he asati kase daro wodeppe kase saloy Xoossa qaalan medhettoyssanne biittayka haaththafenne haaththan dizayssa erishe kaddeettes.\x - \xo 3:5 \xt Medhe 1:6-9\x*
\v 6 He wode diza alamezi haaththan mitetti dhaydes.\x - \xo 3:6 \xt Medhe 7:11\x*
\v 7 Hessaththoka ha7i diza saloynne biittay nagaranchchati dhayana diza pirda gallas gakkanaas tamas giigi uttida.
\p 
\v 8 Ta siiqotoo! Intte gidikko Godaa achchan issi gallassi shii layththa mala; qasseka shii layththi issi gallassa mala gididayssa hessa he hanoza balopite.\x - \xo 3:8 \xt Maza 90:4\x*
\v 9 Issi issi asatas misatiza mala Goday ba yootida hidota qaalaa polanaas gam7ennakoshin asi wurikka maarettana malanne ay asikka dhayontta mala koyidi izi intte gishshas takkees.
\p 
\v 10 Godaa gallassay qasse kayso yeeththa mala qoppontta dishin gakki wodhdhana; he gallas saloti gita giirissan aadhdhana; medheteththi wurikka taman xuugetti dhayana; biittaynne iza bolla dizaazi wurikka xuugettana.\x - \xo 3:10 \xt Mato 24:43; Luqa 12:39; 1Taso 5:2; Ajju 16:15\x*
\v 11 Hessa gishshas heyti wurikka hessaththo dhayanaaz gidikko histtiin intte geeshshateththan Xoossas goynnishe daanaas inttes waani bessennee?
\v 12 Hessa gishshas Xoossa gallassay yaanayssa intte laamotizaytanne izi eleli yaana mala ooththizayta gidite. He gallas saloy taman xuugetti dhayana; medheteththatikka tama seelan seerana.
\v 13 Gido attiin nuni izi nuus immida hidotaa mala xilloteththa oosoy oosettizaso ooraththa salonne ooraththa biitta naagoos.\x - \xo 3:13 \xt Isa 65:17; 66:22; Ajju 21:1\x*
\v 14 Hessa gishshas ta siiqotoo! Hessi wurikka hanana gallas intte naagishe diikko Goday inttena intte bolla borey baynda dishin saroteththan demmana mala minni diite.
\v 15 Nu Godaa dandayay inttena ashshanaas gididayssa intte erite; nu siiqo ishaa Phawuloosi baas imettida erateththa mala izi inttes xaafidayssi hayssa.
\v 16 Izi hayssa ha hanoza gishshas ba kiitatan ubbaan hayssaththoka xaafides; iza kiitata giddon eranaas waayisiza issi issi hanoti deettes; erateththi isttas paccidaytinne nam7u qofan yooqu gizayti hara Geeshsha Maxaafata mirqqizayssaththoka haytakka istti mirqqana; istti hessaththo ooththizay baas dhayanaassa.
\p 
\v 17 Ta ishatoo! Intte qasse hessa kasetidi erida gishshas hankko makkallata balaa gaason gooshetti biidi kase intte minni dizasoppe kundontta mala naagettite.
\v 18 Hessafe bollara nu Godaanne nu dhale Yesus Kirstoosa kiyateththaninne iza shaakki eron pude diccite; izas ha7ikka mernaaskka bonchchoy gido. Amiin.
